      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>diced shallot</strong>,<strong> diced cucumber</strong> and <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>mayo </strong>with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong>, 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>homemade zingy slaw</strong></p>",
